title: Orion
description: Orion is the sixth single by Yonezu Kenshi. It was released on February 15, 2017, and peaked at #3 on the Oricon single chart.

title: Lemon
description: Kenshi Yonezu's "Lemon" is one of the many hits with which he rose to stardom. "Lemon" being his most known song, "Eine Kleine", "LOSER", "Orion" and "Flamingo".

title: Flamingo
description: "Flamingo" and "Teenage Riot" are songs by Japanese singer Kenshi Yonezu, released together as a double A-side single on October 31, 2018.

title: Loser
description: LOSER / Number Nine (LOSER/ナンバーナイン) is the fifth single by Yonezu Kenshi. It was released on September 26, 2016, and peaked at #2 on the Oricon single chart.

title: Uma to Shika
description: "Uma to Shika" (馬と鹿, Horse and Deer) is the 10th single by Kenshi Yonezu. It was released on September 11, 2019.

title: Akogaretekitanda
description: "憧れてきたんだ (Akogaretekitanda)" is song by aimyon from album "Excitement of Youth" released on September 2017.

title: Marigold
description: "マリーゴールド (Marigold)" is song by aimyon released on August 8, 2018
